{"tid":734464,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"周一（9日）：天干屬水地支屬木，水生木之局，反覆上落。","createTime":"2018-07-08T15:47:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T16:04:07.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e2067457d0a0fa6e9324f2c9c2f3e34a2be7c8ce","tid":734464,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T15:47:25.000Z","msg":"周一（壬寅日）：天干屬水地支屬木，水生木之局，反覆上落。<br />\n周二（癸卯日）：天干屬水地支屬木，水生木之局，反覆偏淡。<br />\n周三（甲辰日）：天干屬木地支屬土，木剋土之局，市況出現震盪。<br />\n周四（乙巳日）：天干屬木地支屬火，木生火之局，略作反彈。<br />\n周五（丙午日）：天干地支皆屬火，全火之局，再度回軟。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://money18.on.cc/econ/content.html?section=mktcomm&amp;article_id=bkn-20180708202858771-0708_00842_001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmoney18.on.cc%2Fecon%2Fcontent.html%3Fsection%3Dmktcomm%26article_id%3Dbkn-20180708202858771-0708_00842_001&d=CJMkycaNPSOu6GMVJ4Fa2zPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=b3241657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://money18.on.cc/econ/content.html?section=mktcomm&amp;article_id=bkn-20180708202858771-0708_00842_001</a>"},{"pid":"ab5437fa6ec0da47da9710d869f3c675033ee274","tid":734464,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T15:48:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓豬做乜唔出沈大師個名"},{"pid":"435431988810704c17862ec13326b329b299c9c0","tid":734464,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T16:04:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn.modia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/%E6%B2%88%E7%94%9F-696x392.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.modia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F%25E6%25B2%2588%25E7%2594%259F-696x392.jpg&h=194629c9&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}